name: ResNet-152 for Image Classification
full_description: ResNet-152 is a deep convolutional neural network based on the ResNet architecture, featuring 152 layers. It achieves high performance on image classification tasks by leveraging residual connections to facilitate training deeper networks. ResNet-152 has been widely used in various applications requiring accurate image recognition.
keywords: image classification, deep learning, ResNet, image recognition, convolutional neural network
author: swithana

ai_model.name: ResNet-152
ai_model.description: A deep convolutional neural network model for classifying images, utilizing ResNet architecture with 152 layers for improved feature extraction and classification accuracy.
